Sentencas: Ba1-xSrxCo0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-delta (x = 0.0-0.2) are proposed as the electrodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs) for the first time.
Titulo: Electrochemical performance of Ba0.8Sr0.2Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.925 composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The minimum polarization resistance value is achieved at Ba0.8Sr0.2Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-delta(BSCFN).
Titulo: Electrochemical performance of Ba0.8Sr0.2Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.925 composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this work, BSCFN-xSDC(x = 0-40wt.%) are investigated as the cathodes for IT-SOFCs with SDC electrolyte.
Titulo: Electrochemical performance of Ba0.8Sr0.2Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.925 composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The structures of the cathodes are characterized by X-ray diffraction and SEM.
Titulo: Electrochemical performance of Ba0.8Sr0.2Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.925 composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrode performance of BSCFN-xSDC is measured at various temperatures and oxygen partial pressures.
Titulo: Electrochemical performance of Ba0.8Sr0.2Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.925 composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Comparison of the results demonstrate that introduction of ionic conductive SDC to BSCFN-xSDC composite cathode can make the oxygen reduction reaction processes from the three processes into two processes, the charge transfer process and the adsorption and dissociation of gaseous oxygen process.
Titulo: Electrochemical performance of Ba0.8Sr0.2Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.925 composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The charge transfer process is the major rate limiting step when oxygen partial pressure is higher than 0.05 atm.
Titulo: Electrochemical performance of Ba0.8Sr0.2Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.925 composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The microstructure of BSCFN-30SDC is characterized by more appropriate grain size and more adequate porosity.
Titulo: Electrochemical performance of Ba0.8Sr0.2Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.925 composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The area conductivity of adsorption and dissociation of gaseous oxygen process for BSCFN-30SDC is the highest.
Titulo: Electrochemical performance of Ba0.8Sr0.2Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.925 composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: of single cell results demonstrate that BSCFN-xSDC composite cathode has higher power density than BSCFN cathode.
